<div style="text-align: right;">
<p><span id="u-credit-00210" class="option-button fa fa-info-circle">信息</span><a class="option-button fa fa-edit" href="/log-of-anomalous-items-cn:00210" target="_blank">编辑</a></p>
</div>
<div id="u-credit-00210-hovertip">
<p><strong>作者：</strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/scorpionidaslaughter" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6306406); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6306406&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610202984" alt="ScorpionidaSlaughter" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6306406)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/scorpionidaslaughter" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6306406); return false;">ScorpionidaSlaughter</a></span></p>
<p><strong>发布日期：</strong><span class="odate time_1589639931 format_%25Y-%25m-%25d">16 May 2020 14:38</span></p>
